OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy rain
OL,6,Fclearing southeast across England and
OL,7,FWales tonight. Otherwise clear spells
OL,8,Fand showers, some wintry. More
OL,9,Fpersistent rain and snow over the high
OL,10,Fground in Scotland, where patchy frost
OL,11,Fand ice is also likely. Windy, but
OL,12,Fslowly easing.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FA cold and windy day with a
OL,15,Fmixture of sunshine and blustery
OL,16,Fshowers. Showers merging to give more
OL,17,Fpersistent rain and snow in places,
OL,18,Fsnow most likely over northern hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
